Uses of Package
org.apache.lucene.geo

  • Packages that use org.apache.lucene.geo 
    Package Description
    org.apache.lucene.document
    This package contains several point types: BigIntegerPoint for 128-bit integers LatLonPoint for latitude/longitude geospatial points
    org.apache.lucene.geo
    This package contains geo utility classes: Tessellator for decomposing shapes into a triangular mesh
